Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence... {Your existence. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:11.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will erase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.{...This, I don't know what to say >_>}{Heh. I know what you mean. "I arrived.", perhaps? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:08.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on just cold-heartedly rejecting your friend that came to visit late at night?{Are you planning to just cold heartedly reject your friend that came to visit late at night!}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:10.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have no friends, so go home! {I don't have any friends! Go home! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:12.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! {check}{I think that's what he said, but it went too fast for me to hear}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:15.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay I said! {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.19,0:02:20.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me five minutes. I have to clean my room!{Wait 5 minutes, I have to clean my room!}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to hide your perverted books, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just wait outsi-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:35.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're a manga artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:38.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Currently my active profession.{Aiko:Profession??} {Nat:My profession for now.} {Check?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the reason why you keep on ditching, even though you have such integrity... {This is the reason why you ditch even though you have integrity.}{So this is the reason why you keep on ditching, even though you have integrity... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:49.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, but on one condition...{Yea, but there is one condition.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:50.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:00.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't have any right to talk about my feelings...{I don't really have any eligibility to tell my feelings...}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:05.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:06.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oww~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:15.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that much fun to fool other people? {Does fooling other people really that fun? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you said something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm scouting a female lead actress, the success rate is higher this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "female lead"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.64,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When will this get interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's been like this the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How much of this do I have to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,About two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:42.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show me things that are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for this either.{I'm not that free either./I don't have much spare time either.}{I don't want to be here either.} {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Which parts were boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.27,0:03:48.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where, you say? {"Where", you say. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The actor is clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The story is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It felt interesting at first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It gets boring when you start watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:59.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did it feel interesting in the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,it looked nice on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The acting was clumsy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It felt somewhat like it was full of energy that it was overwhelming. {Somewhat it was full of energy so it was over-whelming.}{- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:11.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You actually have a good eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The direction and the script were done by a senpai in the Film Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I did the filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Good movie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.47,0:04:20.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:23.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Kyousuke wants to film a new work...{Seems like that Kyousoke wants to film a new work.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,with you as the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:31.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be in my movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:36.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The only character that will be introduced will be you, Kei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:39.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right even if you only do it in your spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:41.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I will follow that with my camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:44.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm... only a beginner when it comes to acting. {But... I'm a beginner at acting. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right since there's no script. {That's alright, since there's no script. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:52.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan's moments of life and feelings will be recorded as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,My... feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something like a documentary?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's neither a documentary nor a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This is not with any decisions made...{Without deciding first.}{Just being spontaneous... - megu}{Or... "Without thinking about it..." - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,but instead letting it be preserved on film.{To let it preserve from the taken/filmed material.}{check} {To let it be preserved on/from film. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.39,0:05:09.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that without envisioning it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be held down by any preset expectations.{I don't want to be encased in the vision that was made at first.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:16.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after ideals... will severely limit what I can do.{Chasing only ideals. Cannot produce anything good/Will limit what I can do.}{Check please} { - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:21.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if nothing good comes out of it, there's no point if it isn't a movie I want to film.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking from a professional's perspective... {That's speaking from a professional's perspective. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:27.61,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,creating a work isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:30.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that it's not possible to make it freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:33.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's harder compared to professionals who are sure to get fired.{It's harder than professionals who are sured to get fired.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:36.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Getting fired is what professionals fight against. {Getting fired is what professionals fight against. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from the feeling of freedom that one gets even without fighting.{It has different meanings than from the freedoms that is obtained without even fighting}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The thing I want to fight against is different! {fight against? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.97,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to film without being restricted by the viewers' expectations.{I want to film without being caught in the viewer's views.}{- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you draw only thinking of the readers? {Do you draw only for the readers? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:53.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I do it while drawing what I want to draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:57.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that you have to think of the readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:59.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you film without even thinking of the viewers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay even if it's just one scene. {Just one scene is alright. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.66,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay even if it's just one cut. {Just one cut is alright. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:06.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to film something that will touch the souls of the viewers.{I want to film something that will touch the souls of the people who watches.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And for it to be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:12.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be useless if it isn't a scene that touches my soul!{There is no use if it isn't a scene that touches my soul!}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, then try doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:17.52,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:21.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, don't just decide this on your own.{Hold on, don't just decide this by yourselves.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:24.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that I would be in the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.70,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:31.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless even if you wait, so please just give up.{It's useless even if you wait so please give up.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I will wait for a favorable response. {Then, I'm waiting for a favorable response. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what other people say! {Listen to what other people say! - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:41.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what he is planning to accomplish by filming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you are thinking of making an appearance, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:47.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is quick to act on girls.{kyosuke is a playa}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:50.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're worrying about me.{You're worrying./You're worrying about me.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.18,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.{what ever takes your fancy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:56.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:02.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Does Miyamura-senpai come over often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:04.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Just only two or three times she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:05.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:07.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible...{Possibly...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,annoying?{seperate lines if possible.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:12.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Coming by in the morning to wake you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and nagging you to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:21.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, do you think I'm annoying? {Onii-chan,You don't think I'm annoying?}{- megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? {Comment: Is this line part of the next line or is it a standalone one? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:23.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why so sudden?{So suddenly?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You don't listen even if I say the right things. {check}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't like that back then.{childhood}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,since I'm not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're becoming an adult too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:44.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Renji-kun again...{Again about Renji-kun...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro has a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It looks like she's been having fun recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.16,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:58.33,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say it that way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.76,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If this continues, it might turn out that way.{If this continues, it looks that way.}{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:08.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's a basketball game on Sunday. Will you come and watch? {match -> game? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:14.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,This game I'll definitely win. {I'll definitely win that match. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:21.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell Onii-chan something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Something important? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For now, it's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.96,0:08:27.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did you read it? Chihiro's novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was quite amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How can Chihiro have such...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:45.67,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To Chihiro, writing is the same as living. {To Chihiro, writing is the same as living. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:46.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To transfer the image to a stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:54.21,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,the self of the past and the self of the future who are reading it are different people.{ - megu}{The self of the past, and to the self of the future reading it are different being.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:59.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro is connecting the vanishing past with the future through the diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:05.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's about how much you accurately transfer your image to another person.{To a different being, how accurately can you transfer your image.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.31,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It is same as an author.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro's ability in writing is on the same level as that of a novelist's.{Chihiro's ability to write, is the same as a novelist.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:16.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those abilities supposed to be unable to improve without the ability to remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It might be something that was there already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:23.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she doesn't remember, her body might have possibly learned it.{Even if without remembering, it's possible that the body learned it.}{the writing} { megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,With the determination prepared for death while trying to communicate...{With the determination that's prepared for deathwhile trying to communicate...}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.43,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,it is a strength that appears. {A strength appears. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as this is how it is, let's hope that it will be finished. {the novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san, just what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:43.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Work or everyday life... why are you always at the church? {Your work or your everyday life, or why you are always at church? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a person... I'm waiting for...{A person... I'm waiting for.}{I'm waiting... for a person. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:51.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a priest, nor am I a counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:55.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But after meeting you, take this advice as a guide.{I know the sentence is odd, but I couldn't think of a better way to put it} {check} {But after meeting you, take this advice as a guide. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:57.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too involved with Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.29,0:10:03.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The girl{little girl} started to draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Books, instruments, paintings...{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:12.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In one of those things, there were the tools that made the best humans.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But, it didn't go too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:18.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Many times, I got sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:20.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't really matter even if I got sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,you get sick of getting sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:28.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I started drawing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.92,0:10:33.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that the realistic scenery was directed at myself.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:37.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To write what is there would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:39.82,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For something that's not there...{What is not there.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For humans to write about it... {For humans to write about it... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.09,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,might be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.84,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:49.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything that isn't going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:56.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, about the castle that the girl{little girl} lives in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine the storage too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The storage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:01.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The supply room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The storage with the necessary articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:10.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the book storage where the girl {little girl}reads to gain knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And other things such as the scenery of the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,or the appearance of the wild plants I don't know too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Materials are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a library or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:27.55,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,One is in Otowa, and there's a library at school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What business do you have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.15,0:11:48.73,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the previously boring conversation.{I apologize for the boring conversation previously.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Boring conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:51.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:57.81,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-senpai and I have known each other since childhood.{TL check} {Hirono-senpai and I.. have known each other since childhood. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:59.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.85,0:12:04.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Hirono didn't have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just leave Senpai who was always alone. {I couldn't just leave senpai alone, who was always by himself. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:11.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I took him to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:15.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You suddenly took a boy to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan is very bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:22.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is changing the subject like Miyamura-senpai's specialty? {Is switching subjects around Miyamura-senpai's specialty? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:26.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really follow serious conversations.{well, ain't that nice} {I can actually relate to that.. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:31.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In my room, there were many shoujo manga. {In my room, there was lots of shoujo manga. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:35.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That was the the first source of enjoyment that{object of fun joy or pleasure} Hirono-senpai encountered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:38.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai read with much concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:43.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't think he would become a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:47.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hirono-senpai's talent suddenly grew. {Hirono-senpai's talent suddenly grew. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought about something.  {I thought of something. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To watch someone trying their best...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:54.39,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,and to only think it is amazing was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:59.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that one who tries his best doesn't acknowledge people who do nothing.{Doubtlessly, one who tries don't acknowledge people who doesn't do anything.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:02.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least, I don't think they'll notice them...{at least, I do not think they will take liking.}{people who try} { - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,So is that the reason why Kei-chan started playing basketball?{That will be, the reason why Kei-chan started basketball?}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:11.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Miyamura-senpai said that I picked the wrong place to be honest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For me, Onii-chan is...{someone that I love} {and obviously, we need to censor what she says to create dramaaa~}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Since long ago and even now... {From long ago and until now. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.93,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For now and always... {And from now on and forever. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:25.32,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,whenever I think of him. {Onii-chan}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:30.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Because my feelings never went astray even up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:34.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you say that to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:36.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For you to make it go astray will be fine.{check} {It's alright to let my feelings go astray. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:44.34,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't lose to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:51.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I will erase you from Onii-chan's heart.{That's right, don't take no crap from her Kei >_>b} {I smell an incoming catfight. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.06,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,from Hirono-kun's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,will disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:06.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,From there, I will start over with Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.79,0:14:09.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And with that, farewell to you.{And with that goodbye for you.}{there is got to be a better way of putting this...} { - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And then, the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It will be the end of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:21.41,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear again...{Miyamura}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:27.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone with a uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Like one that's not needed because they graduated.{That's not needed because we graduated.}{the uniform}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.90,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Did it tear anywhere? {the uniform}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:37.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Not for me, but if there is a girl uniform left... {Not for me, but if there's an available female uniform... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for you to ask around in your cooking class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.45,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:44.44,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For Chihiro-chan right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:48.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone keeps their used ones,{uniform} so it shouldn't be a problem.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:53.22,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, if it's about uniforms, Kuze-san also has them.{And the truth comes out... Kuze-san, the cross-dresser...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:56.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The ones I'm talking about are girls' uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.68,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. For girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.42,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,But why... does Kuze-san have them? {Why would Kuze-san have one? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:04.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where did I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:10.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if you don't answer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:14.37,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Kuze-san have such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.67,0:15:17.24,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're male too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:23.03,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,In other words it's a memento, and right now dress when it's important and leave out only half.{check}{I bet it's tled horribly this line...}{Ugh.. I give up on this line... TL check please? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:27.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Although you said it very implicitly, I get it, so it's okay now. {Although you said}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:33.80,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're having Chihiro-chan wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:36.35,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't get any weird ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:39.08,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, so what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Will this size be okay? {Will this size be OK? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:42.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.47,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Size? You have more than one? {the size}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:46.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:49.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.{check}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:54.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:59.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why does my mother know that Kuze-san had girls' uniforms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:05.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they were cute; I really wished that she would wear one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:09.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What did you request to another person's wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, a moment please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:15.01,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Does it not seem to be the right size?{Does the size not fit?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:18.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The size seems fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:22.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the wrong category?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kuze-san, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:28.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,When you say uniform, it's without a doubt this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're really hopeless...{check}{Kuze-san, you're the best >_>b}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I finished changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:42.14,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Otowa's school uniform, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:42.94,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:46.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Onee-chan right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.91,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:53.59,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It fits you really well, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.46,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to school tomorrow with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can't we go right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.98,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I put spirit into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The Miyako Special. Rice topped with barbecued eel.{oh man, those are really good}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.00,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The eel is wasting time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.03,0:17:35.28,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, being free after getting promoted...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:37.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Would an eel be loitering around?!{a word play where Hirono confused hitsumabushi(the rice topped with barbequed eel)}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Rice topped with barbecued eel.{eel is also known the raise the sex drive in guys, so Miyako giving Hirono eel means... Miyako is horny for Hirono?!?} {He'd be feeling reallllly hot afterwards.. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hirono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:47.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have work on weekends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,On Sunday, let's go somewhere to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:55.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,During break, I need to prepare for the next deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:04.10,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I know... that there is a basketball game... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:07.36,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a lie. It's just that I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.07,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then you are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.29,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't promise to go and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:18.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Then, promise with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.51,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,On Sunday, let's go on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.48,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I said that on breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:26.63,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.58,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.15,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Lets go... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Kei-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's still next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:07.05,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.89,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.55,0:19:16.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I said that if you filmed me without my consent, that I'd use my right hand, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.53,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's okay to hit me as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There is a moment that can only be filmed now.{There is a moment where it can be filmed only now.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you miss it, you can't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:28.95,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:32.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I want to film those unaffected things. {fleeting? - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,For that reason, {For that reason. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I take action despite the consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:39.57,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you take action, if you fail that will be the end. {Even if you take an action, that will be the end if you fail. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:43.50,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't give up, there is no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.60,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Time and time again, I'll keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:54.20,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I called him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:58.79,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Some light anemia with dizziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:02.23,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,And also there seemed to be a injury to the knee from the fall. {Say wha? Check} {And seems like there's an injury from the fall. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:03.99,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.51,0:20:06.49,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:13.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I said it's fine. It's embarrassing, so put me down!{smut!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:16.30,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet and stop moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.86,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, doing such stupid things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:21.12,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep on saying "stupid, stupid"?{What, keep saying stupid, stupid.}{ - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,To do it to the point of collapsing is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I just took a slight fall. {I was just a short fall. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:27.72,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter, so stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.71,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.38,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I did no such thing. {pushing herself}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You're always pushing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:35.69,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same as Onii-chan back then. {That's the same old Onii-chan.} {check?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.12,0:20:39.19,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay if it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:42.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How is that so?{What is that.}{tled literal}{How does that work.}{tled symbolic}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:48.54,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan... is wearing nice clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.33,0:20:52.17,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,You had a date with Miyamura-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:54.65,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:56.26,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:59.85,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. There's no way that I can leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.83,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Should I give her a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:05.87,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Aw crap, I forgot my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:07.96,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.25,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.{Kei-chan looks so happy lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:14.75,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Now, didn't you say that you had something to tell me after the game was over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:17.02,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.40,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,School...{she is so mesmerized...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:29.62,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nerve-racking. {nerve racking, I think... - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.27,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. If you just walk casually, no one will notice. {It's alright. If you just walk casually, no one will notice. - megu}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.13,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,How do I usually walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.11,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,There's the scent of books.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.88,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.92,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.78,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,The things I want to convey are not words, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.78,0:23:40.04,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:43.77,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Next {\i1}ef - a tale of memories:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:44.74,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:48.56,ef[Default],,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
